Module instructions
Package fr.project.instructions.simple

Class TypeInstruction

java.lang.Object
fr.project.instructions.simple.TypeInstruction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Instruction
public class TypeInstruction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Instruction
A class that allows to detect and write a type instruction of a .class file. It is stored as an Instruction of a Method.
Author:
CHU Jonathan
